{"_id":"RIyiZa2ptv4sJXRO","name":"Flamme éternelle","type":"spell","img":"icons/sundries/lights/lantern-iron-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Une flamme à la luminosité égale à celle d'une torche embrase soudain l'objet que vous touchez. L'effet du sort ressemble à une flamme ordinaire, mais ne dégage pas de chaleur et ne consomme pas d'oxygène. On peut couvrir ou cacher la flamme éternelle, mais pas l'étouffer ni l'éteindre avec de l'eau.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"perm"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object","range":{"value":"contact"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"Poussière de rubis d'une valeur de 50 po, que le sort consume","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"price":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"3UjVNZPJLHwgrlkI":3},"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-grimoire.7Un5tXCwNRawIQg0"},"betterRolls5e":{"critRange":{"type":"String","value":null},"critDamage":{"type":"String","value":""},"quickDesc":{"type":"Boolean","